{"tid":603983,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人細個成日啪手指？","createTime":"2018-03-24T09:16:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-24T13:23:10.000Z","uid":15842,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"c1000e11f1b031b09266d34cb08936e4640fe973","tid":603983,"uid":15842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T09:16:09.000Z","msg":"小學個時啲同學好鍾意啪到啲手指咔咔聲<br />\n特別係喺女同學面前硬係啪得特別大聲 真係用嚟求偶咁款<br />\n而身邊點都會有唔識啪嘅人同人講啪得多會生骨刺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (包括我)<br />\n但大個咗又唔覺有人會啪手指<br />\n識啪個啲人都好似無晒呢個習慣<br />\n有無人知到底咩事會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3a9b31f4b9d06a5da18d951fbfb003c5ed9ac51","tid":603983,"uid":144784,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T09:17:02.000Z","msg":"睇完個po不由自主咁啪咗下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c632c9fefaba3ef3f4d9d503fa1a5163100f805","tid":603983,"uid":46965,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T09:17:33.000Z","msg":"成日啪 <br />\n特別係啪到最難啪嗰啲關節位 最爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09d010041a405b32d0e7719576a1cdd5f9735cee","tid":603983,"uid":15842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3a9b31f4b9d06a5da18d951fbfb003c5ed9ac51","tid":603983,"uid":144784,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T09:17:02.000Z","msg":"睇完個po不由自主咁啪咗下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T09:24:42.000Z","msg":"你係單手啪定兩隻手咁啪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"299dd7ec1438a6fe03bcd753c88ffedfbbf4c328","tid":603983,"uid":140834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T09:25:28.000Z","msg":"激嬲條女就會俾條女啪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c1b929348cabf00d41df6dcaa9d3fb547495c22","tid":603983,"uid":167674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited